    ## Seek out and learn from people that inspire you

    Seek out and learn from people that inspire you. And these people don't necessarily have to be people you have met or people that are alive or even people that are real.

    I watch a lot of Youtube when I'm struggling through something. Youtube is amazing because it gives you access to a pool of people that you wouldn't normally have access to. People that are better that are way better at life than you in every imaginable way ;-)

    I watch interviews from the Obama, Steve Jobs, Elon Musk, Will Smith and many others to try to figure out what makes them tick.

