    I didn't include this to scare you or depress you, but to pursue your exactly what you want. College is the first time in your life, you start taking the wheel. It doesn't get any easier, in fact, as you get older you just get more responsibility with less safety net. Nothing in this life is a given and it's a waste of time to pursue anything other than your dreams.

    ## Conclusion

    I hope this letter finds you well. I hope you find at least one or two things here that you can apply to your own life. We are all extremely proud of you. We will always have your back no matter what. Have a great 19th birthday Michael.

